Package hr.fer.zemris.java.webserver

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDispatcher
    This interface specifies a method that dispatches a request to a different url, and the class implementing this interface must implement this functionality.
    IWebWorker
    Defines an interface to any object that can process current request, it gets RequestContext and is expected to create content for a client.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DemoRequestContext
    A program that demonstrates the use of RequestContext.
    RequestContext
    The class represent a server response context, that is used for generating response header, cookies and data(html, text, ...).
    RequestContext.RCCookie
    Cookie used to save session's parameters.
    SmartHttpServer
    A simple server capable of loading css - like scripts using SmartScriptEngine, supports both configuration and convention-over-configuration approach and it also provides a simple cookie support.
